{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_03_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 二月のチョコだけが違う",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインデー前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（もうこんな時間か……早く帰ろう）\n（……ん？　まだ誰か残ってるのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Is it that late already? …… Let's go home)\n(…… hmm?　Is there anyone still left?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 12.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "おや、{user}君\nこんな時間まで仕事なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}.\nAre you working until this late?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ。葵も遅くまでお疲れ様\n一人で練習してたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Aoi you're staying up late too tho.\nDid you practice alone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐバレンタインイベントがあるから\nその練習",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a Valentine's Day event coming up soon‚\nso practice for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "本番のステージで、思うように体が動かない\nなんて訳にはいかないからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't have my body not working the way\nI want it to on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "出演が決まった訳じゃないのに\nやる気満々じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not like you've been cast yet‚\nbut you're ready to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね\nこころが凄くやる気になってるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure.\nEven Kokoro is very motivated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、リズノワの頼れる先輩は違うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I'd expect from a reliable senpai at LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "……とはいえ、さすがにもう遅いし\n今日はそろそろ切り上げることにするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it's ……‚ it's late indeed.\nI think it's time to call it a day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら寮まで送るよ。夜道を一人じゃ危険だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll walk you to your dormitory. It's not safe to walk alone at night‚ is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　じゃあせっかくだし\nエスコートをお願いしようかな。頼りにしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?　Well‚ since you're here‚\nI'll ask you to escort me. I'm counting on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.333333399992,
          "startTime": 68.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "もう遅いのに外はまだ人が多いね\n……もぐもぐ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's late and there are still a lot of people outside.\n……yum yum",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきから、何食べてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… What have you been eating for a while now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、これ？　おからクッキーだよ\nカロリー控えめだし、腹持ちがいいからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Oh‚ these?　They're okara cookies.\nThey're low in calories and they're very filling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "レッスン中とかもお腹が空いたら\nこうしてパクパク食べるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever I get hungry‚ even during a lesson‚\nI just gobble it up like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、よく分からないけど\n食べてると莉央が怒るんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you know‚ I don't know‚\nbut Rio gets mad at me when I eat it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "あれはパワハラだね。なんとかしてよ\nおからクッキーが嫌いなのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was power harassment. Do something about it.\nMaybe she doesn't like okara cookies?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、それは……レッスン中だからじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm‚ isn't that because you're in the middle of a …… lesson?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 108.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "この時期はどこもかしこも\nチョコレートのポスターばっかりで、目に毒だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time of year‚\nthere are so many chocolate posters everywhere‚ it's a sight for sore eyes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐバレンタインだから、仕方ないことなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost Valentine's Day‚ so it's not like I have a choice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ははは、葵はそんなに甘い物が好きだったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ Aoi must have liked sweets that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ僕だって、甘いお菓子は嫌いじゃないよ\nチョコだって大好きだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I don't mind sweet treats either.\nI love chocolate‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 132.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "言われてみれば確かに\n莉央さんとパンケーキ食べに行ったりしてたもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yeah‚ it's true that\nRio-san and you used to go out for pancakes‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 138.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（突然黙り込んだな……どうしたんだろう？）",
      "translations": {
